data.description: Live in one unit and rent the other one out! Home with 2 private living units, each with private/separate entrances. The front unit A has 3 bedrooms (one bedroom is presently being used as an office) with a very spacious living room and plenty of storage. The 2nd unit B is also very spacious boasting a side entrance with a nice living room, 1 bedroom, 1 bath with walk in closet, dining area, kitchen, plenty of storage and a screen lanai overlooking the backyard that has ample space for a private pool. This unit has been enjoyed by visiting family and as a seasonal rental. There is a laundry room that is accessible to both units. Across the street is a county park with walking trails, picnic table and a canoe and kayak launching area off Shakett Creek. This property is located within minutes to Nokomis Beach, Nokomis Jetties, historical Venice, Casey Key, and downtown Venice. This location is only steps away from 41 Tamiami Trail, I-75, and the Legacy Trail.
